<plot>Priya wins a cruise abroad a luxury liner en-route from Singapore to India. Shortly after boarding, she meets with artistic playboy, Dev, and both fall in love with each other. Both of them are to marry, but not to each other. Fully aware of this, they part at the end of the cruise, promising to meet again a year later. They go about their respective lives, and it remains to be seen if they will recall their promise or even their romance after the lapse of an year.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?356532</url></doc>
